鐘 都叫做開心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我都可以早日放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢而家話好掛住我<br />\n我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e96a4510da96259aa70c410382f79de50ee394e","tid":12775,"uid":27304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到咁樣 放手都係好事黎<br />\n從你眼中找到了拯救幾秒鐘 都叫做開心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我都可以早日放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢而家話好掛住我<br />\n我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心軟左n次，今次真係軟唔到。<br />\n感覺一直都只係自己係度俾希望自己，<br />\n人地根本無心去為你。<br />\n兩個人一齊，好似得一個人經營，有咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cd3d7d450a8e9924986153ff1cabcda3b091f2","tid":12775,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70aaafd5ceb759e0d764ec95b0dc01fd35bc696c","tid":12775,"uid":8191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"我曾經都以為只要愛就可以忍到可以解決到一切<br />\n天真到以為有一日總會磨合到<br />\n但事實上佢根本唔感激你既付出<br />\n一而再 再而三消耗僅餘既愛情<br />\n<br />\n好彩分手後揾到個願意一齊付出既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0c8e5fa544acdc0f275b089aef489460700404","tid":12775,"uid":27304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全同我男朋友一樣，無論我講咩，佢都覺得我係鬧佢<br />\n我嬲，佢又嬲番我，最後又係我搵番佢<br />\n佢嬲，我嬲佢，最後都係我搵番佢<br />\n<br />\n係條街度嗌交走左去，佢永遠唔會搵番我，sms都唔會有一個，最後我覺得自己都有d錯，就會搵佢話大家都唔啱，但佢仍然會罵我<br />\n佢走左去，最後又係我搵番佢<br />\n<br />\n我講分手，佢又係唔理我<br />\n<br />\n一開始拍拖仲要講勁多大話<br />\n<br />\n我成日諗，呢個男人到底愛我定愛自己。我成日想佢理下我感受，但其實一個會講大話呃你嘅人，又點會知道咩叫人地嘅感受？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同我一樣，係街嗌交會走左去。但佢走就得，如果我走，佢就屌柒我。我成日覺得，我先係男人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de5d05445e7759cf002085565f30dcfb7b97b7a","tid":12775,"uid":34132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:19:31.000Z","msg":"我係你男朋友既角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家真係最後一次分手之後 我先醒覺<br />\n不過一切都太遲了 對方耐性已耗盡<br />\n真係只能夠講抵死"},{"pid":"16fee201361784006062f8fbcb901118a7cdb41a","tid":12775,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6e9934d768255caeec84e3ea616eb7f4a66cc59","tid":12775,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cea90edf845db36df13acecc5569e6292109753e","tid":12775,"uid":27186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"好多人明明理智上都知應該放手，都唔狠心放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得咁辛苦仲要拖落去，拍到一啲都唔開心 有意思咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}